        "id": 1174099
      },
      "writtenOn": "2019-08-22T19:56:32Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "std::vector\u003cuint8_t\u003e is even more significant here because you could insert(). Not only will you avoid many allocations, you’ll avoid all of the copies from the old all_data_ into the new all_data_.",
